room_title: Escape room "The Escape" by The Unlockables in San Diego
room_address: 7380 Clairemont Mesa Blvd Suite 205 San Diego, CA 92111
room_description: Having fun at a fabulous party, you are approached by the host and invited to the VIP area. Once you slip away from the noise, you start to realize that this is no regular party... You've been kidnapped and are now held captive, like many before you. Some of them tried to escape and left clues behind. Can you untangle them and gain the key to your freedom?
